dnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 13.655856, "shard": "09", "shelf_id": "sn84036207, 1910-08-16, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/mthi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["stevensville (mont.)", "stevensville", "hamilton", "hamilton (ravalli county)", "newspapers", "ravalli", "united states", "hamilton (ravalli county, mont.)", "montana"], "subject_headings": ["Stevensville (Mont.)--Newspapers", "Hamilton (Ravalli County, Mont.)--Newspapers", "Montana--Hamilton (Ravalli County)", "Montana--Stevensville", "United States--Montana--Ravalli--Hamilton", "United States--Montana--Ravalli--Stevensville"], "subjects": [{"hamilton": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hamilton&fo=json"}, {"hamilton (ravalli county)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hamilton+%28ravalli+county%29&fo=json"}, {"hamilton (ravalli county, mont.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:hamilton+%28ravalli+county,+mont.%29&fo=json"}, {"montana": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montana&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"ravalli": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ravalli&fo=json"}, {"stevensville": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:stevensville&fo=json"}, {"stevensville (mont.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:stevensville+%28mont.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-07-06T03:58:22.824Z", "title": "The Western news (Stevensville, Mont.), August 16, 1910", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/1910-08-16/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84036207"], "batch": ["mthi_graywolf_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1890", "description": ["Weekly, Nov. 10, 1916-Feb. 24, 1977 -87th year, no. 26 (Feb. 24, 1977). Began in Nov. 1890. \"A progressive newspaper.\" \"Official organ of the Democratic Party in the county.\" Cf. Progressive men of the State of Montana. \"Vigorously anti-[Anaconda] Company.\" Cf. Karlin, J.A. Joseph M. Dixon of Montana. Place of publication varies: published in Stevensville until Aug. 9, 1893 when it moved to Hamilton. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Description based on: Vol. 1, no. 4 (Dec. 16, 1890). Ravalli republican Feb. 1977 (DLC)sn 86075328"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:15.450Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [46.5083709, -114.0938072], "location": ["stevensville", "hamilton", "montana", "ravalli county", "united states", "ravalli"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-114.0938072, 46.5083709], "number": ["1", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "sn84036207", "sn86075328", "library of congress", "596", "2470-4342", "montana hist soc libr", "2025-05-23t21:30:26", "microfilm service copy", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/1910-12-30/ed-1/", "original", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/1900-01-03/ed-1/", "11267479", "2025-06-25t14:22:46", "sn84036204"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "the western news (stevensville, mont.) 1890-1977", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 103.63776, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["stevensville (mont.)", "stevensville", "hamilton", "hamilton (ravalli county)", "newspapers", "ravalli", "united states", "hamilton (ravalli county, mont.)", "montana"], "timestamp": "2026-07-22T07:39:10.628Z", "title": "The Western news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84036207/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218389/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1894", "dates": ["[1894 TO 1899]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. I, no. 1 (Augus 22, 1894); ceased November 24, 1899. Place of publication varies: Stevensville, Aug. 22, 1894-Dec. 7, 1898; Hamilton, Dec. 14, 1898-Nov. 24, 1899. Description based on: Vol. I, no. 1 (Augus 22, 1894); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 4, 2014). Latest issue consulted: Vol. V, no. 20 (December 28, 1898) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 4, 2014). Bitter Root times (Online) Ravalli Republican and Bitter Root times (Online)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:26.498Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2014218389/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["stevensville", "hamilton", "montana", "ravalli county", "united states", "ravalli"], "number": ["online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2373-3667", "2014218389", "880937473"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the ravalli republican (stevensville, ravalli county, montana) 1894-1899 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 94.46214, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["stevensville (mont.)", "stevensville", "hamilton", "hamilton (ravalli county)", "newspapers", "ravalli", "united states", "hamilton (ravalli county, mont.)", "montana"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:50:11.310Z", "title": "The Ravalli Republican", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2014218389/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2015270786/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1890", "dates": ["[1890 TO 1977]"], "description": ["Weekly, Nov. 10, 1916-Feb. 24, 1977 Began in November 1890; ceased February 24, 1977. \"A progressive newspaper.\" \"Official organ of the Democratic Party in the county.\" Cf. Progressive men of the State of Montana. \"Vigorously anti-[Anaconda] Company.\" Cf. Karlin, J.A. Joseph M. Dixon of Montana. Place of publication varies: published in Stevensville until Aug. 9, 1893 when it moved to Hamilton. Description based on: Volume XI, number 9 (January 3, 1900); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 20, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XXI, no. 16 (December 30, 1910) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 20, 2016). Ravalli republican Feb. 1977"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:34.166Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2015270786/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["stevensville", "hamilton", "montana", "ravalli county", "united states", "ravalli"], "number": ["2470-4350", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "online resource", "2015270786", "935363765"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the western news (hamilton, montana) 1890-1977 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 94.46214, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["stevensville (mont.)", "stevensville", "hamilton", "hamilton (ravalli county)", "newspapers", "ravalli", "united states", "hamilton (ravalli county, mont.)", "montana"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:52:54